data.description: Cozy up on the back screened in porch in front of the wood burning fireplace. This 4 bedroom 3 bathroom home has something for everyone. Inside you will find large family room with lots of natural light, spacious dining room as well as flex space, currently being used as home office. Outside features include fenced backyard, quiet corner lot, outdoor storage building. This is a lot of house for the money and wont last long!!
